::Prowl/Firearm::

Prowl looks at Iron Raptor, recieving her thoughts but knowing that 
Firearm had no idea what was going on. He looks at the large Maximal, 
who was looking back and forth from Prowl and Iron Raptor in surprise.

"What happened to you guys?" Firearm asks, looking over at Iris as 
well.

"Long story," Prowl replies, and then asks Iron Raptor's question, 
"Why'd Kluster call a meeting."

Firearm shruggs. "No idea. But we better get to it."

Prowl nods and walks over to Iron Raptor.

-Ready to fly, love?-
